{"tid":673923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警斥2700萬元購3輛水炮車　首輛今抵港","createTime":"2018-05-22T08:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T07:06:06.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ade735013a5d8e24608f5927ddcc225fd63000","tid":673923,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:56:21.000Z","msg":"警隊早前獲立法會撥款斥資2700萬元採購3輛配備噴水裝置、俗稱「水炮車」的群眾管理車輛，據《南華早報》報道稱。首輛水炮車今日(22日)早上已運抵香港，該輛水炮車由德國生產商平治，於法國廠房度身訂造，今早以水路運抵葵涌貨櫃碼頭，落船後已被運往到代理商仁孚行位於上水的商用車維修中心停放。<br />\n<br />\n2014年佔領運動過後，警方斥資2700萬元購入3輛俗稱「水炮車」的群眾管理車輛，並於2015年底招標。根據當時的水炮車招標文件顯示，水炮車最少配備15支不同大小的水炮，車頂兩支主炮，每分鐘各可射出1,200公升水，水壓達1,000千帕，更可環迴360度射水。<br />\n<br />\n另外，水炮車更可射出混有顏料或催淚煙的水劑，亦可噴泡。車內設有空氣過濾系統，防止有毒氣體滲入車身。有工程師曾推算，水炮的水力最高可達200磅，足以將成年人「射到飛起」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/191104/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%A52700%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B3%BC3%E8%BC%9B%E6%B0%B4%E7%82%AE%E8%BB%8A-%E9%A6%96%E8%BC%9B%E4%BB%8A%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F191104%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25A52700%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25B3%25BC3%25E8%25BC%259B%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%2582%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25BC%259B%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=XXRUhZubQJyMGvZDInv0uaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=b83eeca7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/191104/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%A52700%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B3%BC3%E8%BC%9B%E6%B0%B4%E7%82%AE%E8%BB%8A-%E9%A6%96%E8%BC%9B%E4%BB%8A%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2ee345c4de8e6998dc657dc94efd94fc3e124b","tid":673923,"uid":88309,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"全香港啲注意力集中哂喺長洲嘅時候，啲警犬就鬼鬼鼠鼠揀今日送呢架垃圾黎，淨係識做埋啲鼠竊狗偷嘅嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2472bb1f3e7bf6b8c03b8643ddd1bfd9026b26","tid":673923,"uid":52194,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:29:07.000Z","msg":"打撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1838cbe6fa94c2ea11bff5bdf6f48bc0991db250","tid":673923,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff2ee345c4de8e6998dc657dc94efd94fc3e124b","tid":673923,"uid":88309,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"全香港啲注意力集中哂喺長洲嘅時候，啲警犬就鬼鬼鼠鼠揀今日送呢架垃圾黎，淨係識做埋啲鼠竊狗偷嘅嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"有撚人會理咩 <br />\n<br />\n腥港人既想法係 「自己係普通市民 又唔會畀依家車射既  理嚟做乜 ?」"},{"pid":"662efd55e20c54405e7ba02ffda20284e5e981be","tid":673923,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"擋到幾多粒RPG-7<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0017dbe6cb12b8d359495e800e974ef44ba0101","tid":673923,"uid":63944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17b281c879bb8dc313136e213b03930b98cd8714","tid":673923,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f5a66bbdc063eb713c31323a9425a075b8497fb","tid":673923,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"300abc90f7bcbdd4af13711012a8b270e24806eb","tid":673923,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T10:12:34.000Z","msg":"200磅力 近少少都可能直接射穿肉體"},{"pid":"4a2728ccc12573f45e16b59bfd3d0f192a3952b6","tid":673923,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29e7f477d3703f67f